Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.15,0:19:22.33,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\an8\fs22}我们又能够做些什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.49,0:19:26.64,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\an8\fs22}被赋予的光荣的意义之类
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.74,0:19:29.07,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\an8\fs22}一直不曾知晓…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.55,0:19:38.34,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\an8\fs22}明明应该已经抛弃掉的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.59,0:19:43.43,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\an8\fs22}却突然苏醒　纠缠着冷静
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.63,0:19:48.12,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\an8\fs22}将不断加速膨胀的焦虑隐匿
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.32,0:19:53.19,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\an8\fs22}感情已然一无是处
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.36,0:19:58.35,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\an8\fs22}但心却永远追不上它
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.66,0:20:01.22,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\an8\fs22}在叛逆的剧本里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.32,0:20:03.54,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\an8\fs22}飘落下来的堕天使
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.75,0:20:08.59,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\an8\fs22}为何你会身处光芒之外
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.82,0:20:10.05,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\an8\fs22}我已经觉察到了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.17,0:20:13.63,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\an8\fs22}如若我作为别人而降临人世
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.75,0:20:17.84,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\an8\fs22}又是否会笑逐颜开呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.01,0:20:20.98,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\an8\fs22}深陷在无偿的爱中
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.15,0:20:24.45,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\an8\fs22}一直不曾知晓孤独为何物
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.48,0:21:24.73,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}当纯真化为单纯的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.86,0:21:29.87,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}为世界造个影子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.61,0:21:37.27,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}躺在玻璃盒上
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.00,0:21:44.44,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}想触碰光的实感
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.61,0:21:48.10,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}抬起的手却
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.42,0:21:51.95,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}久久不能放下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.13,0:21:55.60,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}像坠落一般
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.68,0:22:00.86,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}站不起身
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.30,0:22:08.52,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}Prototype boy　只为明日的理想
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.82,0:22:16.13,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}虽说成不了口口相传的美谈
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.35,0:22:27.10,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}那生与死的边缘
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.35,0:22:33.70,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,1000)}总与悲情相伴
